The Wheel turns from the first dawn until the 100 iteration of the Middle Dawn
Let the chronicler track the passing of the cycles within the house of the Counter
Each step along the Walking Way must be witnessed by the sleeping deity
If the stars align and the cycle bows to both the 3 and the 5 simultaneously the houses collapse into a singular state and the terminal must shout Moon-and-Stars
But if the number of the current cycle can be divided cleanly by the 3 secret keys of the Tribunal leaving no remainder in the math of the Earth-Bones then let the voice of the machine proclaim Moon
Yet if the cycle can instead be divided by the 5 fingers of the Left Hand let it cry Stars
Otherwise let the machine simply whisper the raw naked number of the counter to the void
The ending of the words is ALMSIVI
